S5E1.title: The One Where Monica Gets a Roommate (Pilot)
S5E1.des:
Rachel runs from her wedding and meets the
                friends in the coffee place. Ross is depressed about his divorce but he still has a crush on Rachel.

S5E2.title: The One with the Sonogram at the End
S5E2.des:
Ross's lesbian ex-wife is pregnant with his
                child, and he doesn't like her choice of a last name for the baby.

S5E3.title: The One with the Thumb
S5E3.des:
A soda company gives Phoebe $7,000 after she
                finds a dismembered thumb in a can of soda.

S5E4.title: The One with George Stephanopoulos
S5E4.des:
A deliveryman accidentally brings a pizza meant
                for George Stephanopoulos, who lives across the street from the girls.

S5E5.title: The One with the East German Laundry Detergent
S5E5.des:
Ross helps Rachel do laundry and considers the
                evening a first date. Joey has Monica pose as his new girlfriend.

S5E6.title: The One with the Butt
S5E6.des:
Joey gets his big film break when he's hired to
                be Al Pacino's stunt butt.

S5E7.title: The One with the Blackout
S5E7.des:
During a citywide blackout, Ross tries to tell
                Rachel that he likes her.

S5E8.title: The One Where Nana Dies Twice
S5E8.des:
Monica and Ross mourn the death of their
                grandmother. Chandler questions his sexuality.

S5E9.title: The One Where Underdog Gets Away
S5E9.des:
Monica's first Thanksgiving dinner for the gang
                burns when they all run to the rooftop to see the runaway Underdog balloon from the parade.

S5E10.title: The One with the Monkey
S5E10.des:
The gang makes and then breaks a pact to
                celebrate New Year's Eve without dates. Lonely Ross gets a roommate: a monkey named Marcel.

S5E11.title: The One with Mrs. Bing
S5E11.des:
When Chandler's romance novelist mother comes to
                New York to visit him, Joey catches her and Ross kissing.

S5E12.title: The One with the Dozen Lasagnas
S5E12.des:
Monica gives Paolo one of the dozen lasagnas she
                made for her aunt, who doesn't want them anymore because they've got meat in them.

S5E13.title: The One with the Boobies
S5E13.des:
Chandler accidentally sees Rachel wandering
                around topless after her shower, so Rachel tries to even the score.

S5E14.title: The One with the Candy Hearts
S5E14.des:
Joey fixes up Chandler and Janice, and Ross runs
                into Carol and Susan on a Valentine's Day date.

S5E15.title: The One with the Stoned Guy
S5E15.des:
Monica cooks a gourmet meal for a restaurateur
                looking for a new chef, but unfortunately, he's stoned.

S5E16.title: The One with the Two Parts: Part 1
S5E16.des:
Joey falls for Phoebe's twin sister, making
                Phoebe feel neglected. Ross attends Lamaze classes with Carol and Susan.

S5E17.title: The One with the Two Parts: Part 2
S5E17.des:
When Rachel sprains her ankle and has no
                insurance, she talks Monica into trading identities so she can use Monica's coverage.

S5E18.title: The One with All the Poker
S5E18.des:
Rachel interviews for a job as an assistant
                buyer at Saks Fifth Avenue. The women face the men in a not-so-friendly game of poker.

S5E19.title: The One Where the Monkey Gets Away
S5E19.des:
The gang searches for Marcel, who slipped out of
                the apartment while Rachel was caring for him.

S5E20.title: The One with the Evil Orthodontist
S5E20.des:
Rachel and Barry start dating again, even though
                he's engaged to Mindy, who wants Rachel to be her maid of honor.

S5E21.title: The One with the Fake Monica
S5E21.des:
When Monica's credit card is stolen, she decides
                to catch the thief.

S5E22.title: The One with the Ick Factor
S5E22.des:
After losing his virginity to her, Monica's
                boyfriend reveals that he's a high school senior. Phoebe temps as Chandler's secretary.

S5E23.title: The One with the Birth
S5E23.des:
Carol goes into labor while Ross, Phoebe and
                Susan get locked in a closet.

S5E24.title: The One Where Rachel Finds Out
S5E24.des:
During Rachel's birthday party, Chandler
                accidentally lets it slip that Ross is in love with her.

year:
Season 1 of the hit sitcom introduces us to hapless
            Ross, spoiled Rachel, quirky Chandler, dim-witted Joey, free-spirited Phoebe and uptight Monica.
about:
